# Accessibilità WCAG 2.2+ – Best Practice 2025

## Principi chiave

- Skip links visibili e focusabili
- Indicatori focus custom (outline ≥2px, contrasto ≥3:1)
- Navigazione tastiera completa (tabindex, focus trap)
- Supporto `prefers-reduced-motion` e alternative statiche
- Live region ARIA per annunci dinamici
- Landmark semantici (`header`, `nav`, `main`, `aside`, `footer`)
- High contrast e dark mode via CSS variables
- Form error handling con aria-describedby
- Lazy loading accessibile e loading state annunciato
- Test automatici con axe-core

## Esempi essenziali

### Skip Links

```html
<div class="skip-links">
  <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Salta al contenuto principale</a>
  <a href="#navigation" class="skip-link">Salta alla navigazione</a>
</div>
```

### Focus Indicator

```css
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}
```

### Live Region (screen reader)

```vue
<div aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true" class="sr-only">{{ announcement }}</div>
```

### Reduced Motion

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

### High Contrast

```css
@media (prefers-contrast: high) {
  :root {
    --color-focus: #ff0000;
  }
}
```

